graph LR
    Kueue[Kueue Operator<br/>v0.6.2]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    Kueue -->|platform| Kubernetes[Kubernetes 1.22+<br/>Required]
    Kueue -->|TLS certs| CertManager[cert-manager or internal-cert<br/>One Required]
    Kueue -->|controller framework| ControllerRuntime[controller-runtime v0.17.0<br/>Required]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    Kueue -.->|metrics| Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>Optional]
    Kueue -.->|autoscaling| ClusterAutoscaler[cluster-autoscaler<br/>Optional]

    %% Job Framework Integrations (Optional)
    Kueue -.->|training jobs| KubeflowTraining[kubeflow/training-operator v1.7.0<br/>Optional<br/>TFJob, PyTorchJob, MXJob, etc.]
    Kueue -.->|MPI jobs| MPIOperator[kubeflow/mpi-operator v0.4.0<br/>Optional]
    Kueue -.->|Ray workloads| KubeRay[ray-project/kuberay v1.1.0-alpha.0<br/>Optional]
    Kueue -.->|multi-job sets| JobSet[jobset v0.3.1<br/>Optional]

    %% Internal RHOAI Dependencies
    Kueue -->|CRD watch/webhook| KubeflowOperator[Kubeflow Training Operator<br/>Internal RHOAI]
    Kueue -->|CRD watch/webhook| RayOperator[Ray Operator<br/>Internal RHOAI]

    %% Integration Points (consumers of Kueue)
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>Internal RHOAI] -.->|UI management| Kueue
    Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines<br/>Internal RHOAI] -.->|auto deploy jobs| Kueue

    %% API Dependencies
    Kueue -->|WATCH/PATCH/UPDATE| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]

